<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>223</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men yào chēng sòng yé hé huá yīn tā dé shèng yǒng yuǎn dé shèng
 jiāng fǎ lǎo de chē liàng hé mǎ bīng tóu zài hǎi zhōng tóu zài hǎi zhōng
 shéi néng dǐ dǎng yé hé huá shéi néng gōng jī tā de bǎi xìng
 zuò zhe wèi wáng zhí dào yǒng gǔ tā de míng shì yīng dāng chēng sòng.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men yào chēng sòng yé hé huá 迦南223</title>
</song>